Metadata: Careers in Science (Salmon Research): Jen Krajcik (Webinar November 4, 2020)
Careers in Science Investigation Webinar November 4, 2020, Corvallis, Oregon.
Oregon Sea Grant and published on YouTube December 14, 2020
This career webinar is for students in grades 6-12 who want to explore careers in marine science. It features Jen Krajcik, manager of the Oregon Hatchery Research Center in Alsea.
